data.description: This is a gorgeous, upgraded, and spacious home nestled in a gated community that features a basketball court, park for pets and family, BBQ’s and entertainment. The open floor-plan and dual family rooms allow for many activities.  There is a bedroom and full bathroom downstairs.  Upgraded stair rails, granite counter tops, walk in pantry, large kitchen island, and much more!  As you go upstairs, and you will find the spacious primary bedroom with a large attached balcony, fireplace, dual closets, and a separate shower and tub.  There are also 2 oversized bedrooms and a HUGE loft/game room! The large backyard with turf and a covered balcony is perfect for entertainment and a little bit of sunshine or shade. Come take a look! You won’t be disappointed!
